  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK718">
<l>uṇarvatu uṭaiyārmuṉ collal vaḷarvataṉ</l>
<l>pāttiyuḷ nīr corintaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lecturing to those who have the ability to understand (for themselves) is like watering a bed of plants that are growing (of themselves).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
